#: skgbankmodeler/sources/org.kde.skrooge-source-boursorama.json
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"You can get the list of available quotes from <a href=\"https://boursorama."
"com/bourse/\">Boursorama</a>.<br/>Then, enter the symbol of the expected "
"quotes."
msgstr ""
"Seznam razpoložljivih kotacij lahko dobite pri <a href=\"https://boursorama."
"com/bourse/\">Boursorama</a>.<br/>Nato vnesite ime ali simbol pričakovanih "
"kotacij."

#: skgbankmodeler/sources/org.kde.skrooge-source-coinmarketcap.json
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"You can get the list of available quotes from <a href=\"https://"
"coinmarketcap.com\">CoinMarketCap</a>.<br/><br/>Then, you must create an "
"account to get an API key and set it in setting.<br/>Then, enter the "
"expected quote in expected currency. Example: if you want BTC in USD, you "
"must enter BTC-USD."
msgstr ""
"Seznam razpoložljivih kotacij lahko dobite pri <a href=\"https://"
"coinmarketcap.com\">CoinMarketCap</a>.<br/><br/>Nato morate ustvariti račun, "
"da dobite ključ API in nastavite v nastavitvah.<br/>Nato vnesite pričakovano "
"kotacijo v pričakovani valuti. Primer: če želite BTC v USD, morate vnesti "
"BTC-USD."

#: skgbankmodeler/sources/org.kde.skrooge-source-cryptocompare.json
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"You can get the list of available quotes from <a href=\"https://www."
"cryptocompare.com/\">CryptoCompare</a>.<br/>Then, you must create an account "
"to get an API key and set it in setting.<br/>Then, enter the <expected "
"quote>-<in the expected currency>. Example: if you want BTC in USD, you must "
"enter BTC-USD."
msgstr ""
"Seznam razpoložljivih kotacij lahko dobite pri <a href=\"https://www."
"cryptocompare.com/\">CryptoCompare</a>.<br/>Nato morate ustvariti račun, da "
"dobite ključ API in nastaviti v nastavitvah.<br/>Nato vnesite <pričakovano "
"kotacijo>-<v pričakovani valuti>. Primer: če želite BTC v USD, morate vnesti "
"BTC-USD."

#: skgbankmodeler/sources/org.kde.skrooge-source-exchangeratesapi.io.json
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"[DEPRECATED: Prefer exchangerates_apilayer.com]. You can get the list of "
"available quotes from <a href=\"https://exchangeratesapi.io/"
"\">exchangeratesapi.io</a>.<br/><br/>Then, you must create an account to get "
"an API key and set it in setting.<br/>Then, enter the expected quote in "
"expected currency. Example: if you want BTC in USD, you must enter BTC-USD."
msgstr ""
"[ZASTARELO: preferirajte exchangerates_apilayer.com]. Seznam razpoložljivih "
"kotacij lahko dobite na <a href=\"https://exchangeratesapi.io/"
"\">exchangeratesapi.io</a>.<br/><br/>Potem morate ustvariti račun, da dobite "
"API ključ in ga nastavite v nastavitvah.<br/>Nato vnesite pričakovano "
"kotacijo v pričakovani valuti. Primer: če želite BTC v USD, morate vnesti "
"BTC-USD."

#: skgbankmodeler/sources/org.kde.skrooge-source-exchangerates_apilayer.json
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"You can get the list of available quotes from <a href=\"https://"
"exchangeratesapi.io/\">exchangeratesapi.io</a>.<br/><br/>Then, you must "
"create an account on <a href=\"https://apilayer.com\">https://apilayer.com</"
"a> to get an API key and set it in setting.<br/>Then, enter the expected "
"quote in expected currency. Example: if you want BTC in USD, you must enter "
"BTC-USD."
msgstr ""
"Seznam razpoložljivih kotacij lahko dobite na <a href=\"https://"
"exchangeratesapi.io/\">exchangeratesapi.io</a>.<br/><br/>Potem morate "
"ustvariti račun na <a href=\"https://apilayer.com\">https://apilayer.com</"
"a>, da pridobite ključ API in ga nastavite v nastavitvah.<br/>Nato vnesite "
"pričakovano kotacijo v pričakovani valuti. Primer: če želite BTC v USD, "
"morate vnesti BTC-USD."

#: skgbankmodeler/sources/org.kde.skrooge-source-grandtrunk.json
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"You can get the list of supported currencies from <a href=\"https://"
"currencies.apps.grandtrunk.net/currencies\">here</a>.<br/>Then, enter the "
"expected currency."
msgstr ""
"Seznam podprtih valut lahko dobite <a href=\"https://currencies.apps."
"grandtrunk.net/currencies\">tukaj</a>.<br/>Nato vnesite pričakovano valuto."

#: skgbankmodeler/sources/org.kde.skrooge-source-skrooge.json
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"You can find the list of available quotes <a href=\"https://skrooge.org/data"
"\">here</a>.<br/>Don't put the csv extension.<br/>In some case (eg. "
"inflation), you will have to remove already downloaded values to download "
"them again."
msgstr ""
"Seznam razpoložljivih kotacij najdete <a href=\"https://skrooge.org/data"
"\">tukaj</a>.<br/>Ne vstavljajte pripone csv.<br/>V nekaterih primerih (npr. "
"inflacija), boste morali odstraniti že prenesene vrednosti, da jih znova "
"prenesete."

#: skgbankmodeler/sources/org.kde.skrooge-source-stooq.json
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"You can get the list of available quotes from <a href=\"https://stooq.pl"
"\">Stooq</a>.<br/>Then, enter the symbol of the expected quotes."
msgstr ""
"Seznam razpoložljivih kotacij lahko dobite pri <a href=\"https://stooq.pl"
"\">Stooq</a>.<br/>Nato vnesite simbol pričakovanih kotacij."

